---
/**
 * Additional rich content sections for the homepage.
 * These supplement the CMS-driven content areas with curated, static sections
 * that match the Rabobank design language.
 */
---

<!-- Wees alert - Fraud Awareness Section -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-12 md:py-16" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="w-full md:w-5/12 flex-shrink-0">
            <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581579438747-104c53d7fbc4?w=600&h=450&fit=crop&crop=faces"
                alt="Persoon leest op de bank"
                class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto object-cover shadow-lg"
                loading="lazy"
                width="600"
                height="450"
            />
        </div>
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div class="w-full md:w-7/12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold italic text-base-content mb-4">
                Wees alert
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Steeds vaker raken organisaties betrokken bij datalekken. En zodra jouw
                gegevens op straat liggen, staan criminelen klaar om toe te slaan: via slimme
                phishingtrucs, een telefoontje van een 'bankmedewerker' die net echt klinkt of
                een ogenschijnlijk nette betalingsherinnering. Door bewust te blijven, houd je
                zelf de controle over je eigen veiligheid.
            </p>
            <a
                href="/en/veilig-online-bankieren/"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-semibold hover:underline transition"
            >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                    <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"></path>
                </svg>
                Herken en voorkom fraude
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Rabo App Promotion Section -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 md:py-12" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
    <div class="bg-neutral text-neutral-content rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold italic mb-4">
                    Bankzaken regel je met de Rabo App
                </h2>
                <p class="opacity-80 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
                    Spontaan uit eten vanavond? Check direct in de Rabo App
                    hoe je ervoor staat.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-success flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                        <span>Altijd en overal toegang tot je bankzaken</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-success flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                        <span>Handige tips en features</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-success flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                        </svg>
                        <span>Uitgebreide online omgeving</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/betalen/rabo-app/" class="btn btn-primary">
                    Lees meer
                </a>
            </div>
            <!-- Phone Mockup -->
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center items-end p-8 md:p-0">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=500&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center"
                    alt="Rabo App op smartphone"
                    class="w-full max-w-sm md:max-w-md h-auto object-cover rounded-t-2xl md:rounded-none md:rounded-tr-2xl"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="500"
                    height="600"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Quick Tips / Financial Insights Section -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-12 md:py-16" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-base-content">Financieel inzicht</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-2 text-lg">Tips en artikelen om slimmer met geld om te gaan</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <a href="/en/eerste-huis-kopen-tips/" class="card bg-base-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <figure class="overflow-hidden">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560518883-ce09059eeffa?w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
                    alt="Eerste huis kopen"
                    class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="400"
                    height="250"
                />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Eerste huis kopen?</h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">
                    Alles wat je moet weten over het kopen van je eerste woning, van hypotheek tot notaris.
                </p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-2">
                    <span class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold group-hover:underline">Lees meer &rarr;</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <a href="/en/sparen-of-beleggen/" class="card bg-base-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <figure class="overflow-hidden">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579621970563-ebec7560ff3e?w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
                    alt="Sparen of beleggen"
                    class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="400"
                    height="250"
                />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Sparen of beleggen?</h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">
                    Ontdek wat het beste bij jouw situatie past en hoe je je geld slim kunt laten groeien.
                </p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-2">
                    <span class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold group-hover:underline">Lees meer &rarr;</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <a href="/en/duurzaam-beleggen/" class="card bg-base-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
            <figure class="overflow-hidden">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1473186578172-c141e6798cf4?w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
                    alt="Duurzaam beleggen"
                    class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
                    loading="lazy"
                    width="400"
                    height="250"
                />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-lg">Duurzaam beleggen</h3>
                <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm">
                    Investeer in een betere toekomst. Ontdek hoe duurzaam beleggen werkt bij Rabobank.
                </p>
                <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-2">
                    <span class="text-primary text-sm font-semibold group-hover:underline">Lees meer &rarr;</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>
